{"tid":406208,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"感受水龍敬樂園的美，水龍敬個人畫展10月14日舉辦","createTime":"2017-09-19T12:42:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-19T17:36:12.000Z","uid":75050,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fcc438012b91edc35537488630d1376e277c1466","tid":406208,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T12:42:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkacger.com/archives/43586\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Farchives%2F43586&d=RwxKApIyLqjTLCqDI3HY%2BvM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=87d24ab9\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkacger.com/archives/43586</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/heyOdP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FheyOdP.jpg&h=c4ceecb8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n感受水龍敬樂園的美，水龍敬個人畫展10月14日舉辦<br />\n<br />\n作者: ACGER編輯部 日期: 19/09/2017 新聞動態<br />\n<br />\n原文授權轉載自ACGdoge<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/TDwQKL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FTDwQKL.jpg&h=c7d4dcb0&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最近R18漫畫水龍敬筆下的知名作品《水龍敬樂園》又是改編成遊戲又是改編為裡番動畫，老師達成了自己的作品被改編為真人愛情動作片、動畫、遊戲的成就<br />\n<br />\n而水龍敬的個人畫展『水龍敬樂園的世界』將在秋葉原舉辦，展期由10月14日至10月23日<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/NUCMsp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FNUCMsp.jpg&h=3c9bc0df&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n水龍敬於1983年出生，大學就讀於早稻田大學，在大學期間水龍敬就開始畫R18同人本，2006年水龍敬參加成人向漫畫精選集《闘姫陵辱》，正式作為R18漫畫家出道<br />\n<br />\n大學畢業後水龍敬作為系統工程師加入某IT企業，在工作期間由於缺乏運動再加上壓力大身體成功增加20公斤，後來水龍敬覺得再也不能這樣活下去，2009年離開了公司專職作為畫師活動<br />\n<br />\n2014年的時候水龍敬發售了自己作為R18漫畫家的首個單行本《貞操觀念 ZERO》，這部作品由於當時大人氣被改編成為了真人愛情動作片，還製作成遊戲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/DMBVbX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FDMBVbX.jpg&h=8338b7f5&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">更有趣的是傳聞水龍敬由於自己老婆的要求畫《刀劍亂舞》的R18本，之前水龍敬甚至接下了BL向遊戲的原畫工作，作為男性R18漫畫家少有地連腐向領域都涉及</span><br />\n<br />\n水龍敬對自己的個人畫展的感想是，原本對自己的畫作沒什麼自信，比起畫師更多是專注在漫畫家活動上，不過回顧了自己的職業生涯也接受了相應的插畫工作，這次的個人畫展將會在不會污染大家眼睛的範圍中挑選展覽作品<br />\n<br />\n水龍敬個人畫展詳細資料：<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.toranoana.jp/21804\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.toranoana.jp%2F21804&d=RwxKApIyLqjTLCqDI3HY%2BvM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=98d10a59\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.toranoana.jp/21804</a>"},{"pid":"4668017d2f6f755b110ddc604d0ca890e022c284","tid":406208,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T12:43:11.000Z","msg":"連水龍敬都有老婆 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46eb7c73c7a1ca0c03b9c8740064b623f5d558da","tid":406208,"uid":30745,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T12:45:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連水龍敬都有老婆 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n懷疑槍間家就係反映佢家室嘅情況"},{"pid":"85e71b00fe9b99bf9dfc1477c829816a2dd0949a","tid":406208,"uid":52194,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T12:45:23.000Z","msg":"BL不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1013ff6ed5e2b52ee8f48be8cfc0a9e573d20864","tid":406208,"uid":75050,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T12:46:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/SjWcUF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FSjWcUF.jpg&h=54ff8af7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae8687eb285ff61e409f6a8f1a481f22e5d37d0b"